text: (Yo artha sunera) rajale adesa diyoh ‘‘ki yusuphala'i mero pasama lya'u.’’ Jaba sandesabahaka unako pasama gayo ta unale bhaneki aphno malikako samu pharkera ja'u ra tinisita sodha ki ti a'ima'iharuko vastavika hala ke cha, jasale ki aphna hata kateka thi'in. Nihsandeha mero palanakarta tiniharuko sadyantrala'i ramrari jandacha
